{"tid":935603,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人屈hi花左佢架車","createTime":"2018-12-10T06:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T12:41:39.000Z","uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d97827b922c9897f3e2f0f7e7c1a72c7d0b0abf6","tid":935603,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"利申 幫同事問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說早兩日揸左地盤判頭架車出去做野 （架車成日出入地盤已經有好多花凹位）<br />\n之後停低左係某個彎彎地既停車位 前面就有架Volkswagen <br />\n開車走既時候發現車頭唔夠位 咁我都倒左兩、三次車<br />\n 夠位出既時候 前面架福士就打右燈 我就即刻停低讓佢出先啦 之後佢就落車行埋黎話我整花左佢架車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSiZ35D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSiZ35D.png&h=de378f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我肯定冇掂過佢架車 <br />\n佢竟然開口話要$2000 和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我冇做過 緊係唔制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是就報警 落左口供 影哂相<br />\n問題就黎啦<br />\n警察今日打黎話 要度下兩部車花痕既高度對唔對位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我部車本身已經咁多花痕 會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條福士女司機仲話如果依加要和解就$4000<br />\n<br />\n想問下依加應該和解定點好 因為上網睇左好多case都係俾錢和解就算 但冇做過都要俾錢真係dum哂春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec91977297be38534f845a2d87f594193e33aa7d","tid":935603,"uid":44489,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"無做就無做 唔洗驚"},{"pid":"e8e999dca5262b6fd0458061b6b7965487827078","tid":935603,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩? 無做過認乜撚 叫佢刮埋花痕啲油去驗添呀"},{"pid":"0c68b7fe4ef027ffc65fdd642c73eb776453929d","tid":935603,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af48d52258719fd09d155f266e0818174bd4497","tid":935603,"uid":29523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"對油對高度，基本程序黎姐<br />\n意外後有報警，咪慢慢打官司囉"},{"pid":"166dba661cb96a5ef623c33985dc95374962f6f8","tid":935603,"uid":196924,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"報警咪報警<br />\n你架車本身愈花愈好, 佢根本冇證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ef5d715961efe9469d3d76b41799c2ce13e043","tid":935603,"uid":207254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"車cam呢"},{"pid":"f20fa0d4db4e427afbff6978f42b53f8f3ee8f3d","tid":935603,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"b5ef5d715961efe9469d3d76b41799c2ce13e043","tid":935603,"uid":207254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"車cam呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"雙方都冇車cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9df937568496a13ae07c79001f610d07d472aea","tid":935603,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e999dca5262b6fd0458061b6b7965487827078","tid":935603,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩? 無做過認乜撚 叫佢刮埋花痕啲油去驗添呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"依加就係諗住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢仲話$4000都俾少佢 真係谷鬼氣"},{"pid":"3d2dd2148a288eb9ee19ad4b07f407aa48416287","tid":935603,"uid":33004,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f20fa0d4db4e427afbff6978f42b53f8f3ee8f3d","tid":935603,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"b5ef5d715961efe9469d3d76b41799c2ce13e043","tid":935603,"uid":207254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"車cam呢"},"citedBy":