pid":"1e0f5e2b405f89437d1783510a117809db4ebffa","tid":935603,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"一架私家車撞到野的話會大聲到你唔信<br />\n正常有用心揸車嘅司機唔會唔知"},{"pid":"47d6a53a4e4d969acc8203ca2378fee0ae69b5cf","tid":935603,"uid":30644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"撞左都唔一定要認啦，冇撞就唔該理直氣壯啲。<br />\n大家架車都花嘅唔可以係對方撞你嘅咩"},{"pid":"81bef3d20f00ac47c77f97257935c2eae8e971e9","tid":935603,"uid":82255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"咪撚認阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 企撚硬咪比錢人洗"},{"pid":"814d94c812d4f4069e394eafd34f75d134ae0aea","tid":935603,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"之前同人撞左和解唔到，即場報埋警現場落左份簡單口供，個時慈母就交通部會再約我落正式口供，到而家三個月麥聲氣都無。打過幾次去問，一係就話負責個慈母放假，一係就出左去做野，有次打去問應機個慈母仲話無咁快，起碼排五六個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n巴打真係幾日前撞咁快有慈母跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2023385499ac75ec7eaddaa9c969677bbecdac43","tid":935603,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n警察果度開左file架車如果拎去賣仲轉唔轉到名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efd121276bb7d4c4f5288836757f668c1997204","tid":935603,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"mr：冇做過點認姐"}]}